item.title: Reference
item.content:encoded:
An obvious reference to the Star Fox video game series in which one of the characters say "Do a Barrel Roll!". Which has become quite the internet phenomenon.

Which in itself is based on the real thing: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barrel_Roll
